        <!-- Function Texts -->
        <text name="function_roofSolarPanelsOption" text="This building has an option to add solar panels on its roof. Price per panel: 265 $. Income per panel, per month: 21,6 $ (with adequate weather conditions)." />
        <text name="function_heiferStable" text="This shelter is intended for heifers. Here they can grow up and then they should be moved to other cow barn. Cows in this shelter does not produce milk and liquid manure, but they still produce manure." />
        <text name="function_cowYoungShelter" text="This shelter is intended for calves or heifers. Here they can grow up and then they should be moved to other cow barn. Cows in this shelter does not produce milk and liquid manure, but they still produce manure." />
        <text name="function_calfHut" text="This hut is intended for calves only. Here they can grow up and then must be moved to other cow barn. Cows in this enclosure does not produce milk and liquid manure, only manure and they requrie a lot of manual daily care!" />
        <text name="function_bunkerSiloCC" text="This bunker silo can be filled witch chaff, grass, alfalfa and clover. After compacting and covering the silo, the content converts into silage. NOTE: If using Maize Plus mod it changes functionality of this silo to M+ standards." />
        <text name="function_grainStorage" text="This multi purpose facility has big storage hall allowing you to store crops on ground or keep before they are processed, plenty of room even for vehicles. Shredder makes food for your animals. Grain can be also stored in large capacity silos." />
        <text name="function_fillableLiquidFertilizerAndHerbicideTanks" text="These tanks can be filled with liquid fertilizer and herbicide." />
        <text name="function_baleStorageCC" text="This building can be used to store your bales." />
        <text name="function_palletStorage" text="This building can be used to store your pallets." />
        <text name="function_orchard" text="Orchard produce fruits. Need Water, Liquid Fertilizer and Compost." />
        <text name="function_greenhouseAdvanced" text="Advanced greenhouse produce vegetables faster but requires more care - Need: Water, Liquid Fertilizer and Compost." />
        <text name="function_compostSilo" text="A compost silo can be filled with organic waste. After compacting and covering the silo, the content converts into compost." />
        <text name="function_compost" text="Compost is required in orchards and greenhouses. Can be used also as fertilizer on field." />
        <text name="function_heapSpawnerStoneCC" text="Stones can be collected free of charge from this building. Produces 3000 units of stone per hour."/>
        <text name="function_heapSpawnerLimestone" text="Limestones can be collected free of charge from this building. Produces 2800 units of limestone per hour."/>
